        "en": "Chapter 1: Import Contract",
        "zh": "第 1 章：导入契约"
      },
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "sample-ch01-s01",
          "page": 1,
          "level": 1,
          "title": {
            "en": "What the Agent Receives",
            "zh": "Agent 接收什么"
          },
          "content": {
            "en": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-en-001",
                "kind": "heading",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "What the Agent Receives"
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-en-002",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "An import request describes the book identity, source files, rights status, language pair, and review gates before any runtime package is generated."
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-en-003",
                "kind": "termNote",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "Import contract: a machine-readable agreement that tells the Agent what inputs are allowed and which checks must pass."
              }
            ],
            "zh": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-zh-001",
                "kind": "heading",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "Agent 接收什么"
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-zh-002",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "导入请求会先描述教材身份、源文件、权利状态、语言组合和人工审核门槛，然后才允许生成运行时教材包。"
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s01-zh-003",
                "kind": "termNote",
                "page": 1,
                "text": "导入契约：一种机器可读约定，用来告诉 Agent 哪些输入可以使用，以及哪些检查必须通过。"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sample-ch01-s02",
          "page": 2,
          "level": 2,
          "title": {
            "en": "Human Review Gates",
            "zh": "人工审核门槛"
          },
          "content": {
            "en": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s02-en-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 2,
                "text": "A public book must pass copyright, table-of-contents, image quality, terminology, and bilingual alignment review before it is added to the catalog."
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s02-en-002",
                "kind": "listItem",
                "page": 2,
                "text": "Blocked or unknown rights keep the book out of the public runtime package."
              }
            ],
            "zh": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s02-zh-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 2,
                "text": "公开教材必须先通过版权、目录、图片质量、术语词典和中英对齐审核，之后才能加入教材目录。"
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch01-s02-zh-002",
                "kind": "listItem",
                "page": 2,
                "text": "权利状态未知或被阻断的内容不得进入公开运行时教材包。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "assets": []
    },
    {
      "id": "sample-ch02",
      "chapter": 2,
      "pageStart": 3,
      "pageEnd": 5,
      "title": {
        "en": "Chapter 2: Runtime Package",
        "zh": "第 2 章：运行时教材包"
      },
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "sample-ch02-s01",
          "page": 3,
          "level": 1,
          "title": {
            "en": "Stable Anchors",
            "zh": "稳定锚点"
          },
          "content": {
            "en": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s01-en-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 3,
                "text": "Every section and content block receives a stable identifier so language switching, notes, vocabulary, and return-to-source actions can keep their place."
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s01-en-002",
                "kind": "table",
                "page": 3,
                "rows": [
                  ["Runtime field", "Purpose"],
                  ["bookId", "Separates learning data by textbook"],
                  ["blockId", "Restores the same semantic block after switching language"]
                ]
              }
            ],
            "zh": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s01-zh-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 3,
                "text": "每个章节和内容块都会获得稳定标识，因此语言切换、笔记、词本和回到原文都能尽量保持当前位置。"
              },
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s01-zh-002",
                "kind": "table",
                "page": 3,
                "rows": [
                  ["运行时字段", "用途"],
                  ["bookId", "按教材隔离学习数据"],
                  ["blockId", "切换语言后回到同一个语义块"]
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sample-ch02-s02",
          "page": 4,
          "level": 2,
          "title": {
            "en": "Dictionary Scope",
            "zh": "词典范围"
          },
          "content": {
            "en": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s02-en-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 4,
                "text": "Each book may carry a small curated glossary first. A larger learner dictionary can be layered later when the source allows it."
              }
            ],
            "zh": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s02-zh-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 4,
                "text": "每本教材可以先携带小型人工术语表；如果来源允许，再叠加更大的学习词典。"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sample-ch02-s03",
          "page": 5,
          "level": 2,
          "title": {
            "en": "Validation Output",
            "zh": "验证输出"
          },
          "content": {
            "en": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s03-en-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 5,
                "text": "The import validator checks schema shape, page continuity, safe asset paths, unique lookup keys, unique book identifiers, and catalog visibility."
              }
            ],
            "zh": [
              {
                "id": "sample-ch02-s03-zh-001",
                "kind": "paragraph",
                "page": 5,
                "text": "导入验证器会检查 schema 结构、页码连续性、安全图片路径、唯一 lookup key、唯一 bookId，以及是否进入主页目录。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
